OL,3,CMade by a Stone! The artwork by Ronnie
OL,4,CWood that's on display at Longleat
OL,6,FRolling Stones legend Ronnie Wood is
OL,7,Fsharing his passion for making art
OL,8,Fwith visitors to one of Wiltshire's
OL,9,Fbiggest tourist attractions.
OL,11,FThe guitarist has loaned a one-tonne
OL,12,Frotating bronze sculpture to Longleat,
OL,13,Fwith the artwork on display in the
OL,14,Festate's Secret Garden.
OL,16,FThe sculpture is called 'Struggles and
OL,17,FTriumphs', and was created in a
OL,18,Ffoundry from an original smaller piece
OL,19,Fcreated by Ronnie in one afternoon.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
