OL,3,CMade by a Stone! The artwork by Ronnie
OL,4,CWood that's on display at Longleat
OL,6,FRonnie said: "It came about on a whim
OL,7,Fas I love horses and I completed it in
OL,8,Fone sitting. It was in the foundry for
OL,9,Fthree to six months; they suggested
OL,10,Frotating it and I thought what a
OL,11,Fbrilliant idea."
OL,13,FRonnie, who is renowned for his art as
OL,14,Fwell as his music, said: "When I heard
OL,15,Fit would be in the Secret Garden, I
OL,16,Fwas very excited. It was perfect for
OL,17,Fit. It means a lot to have it here at
OL,18,FLongleat; it's another bit of history
OL,19,Fin this environment.
OL,26,@nD@NOUsD@PO]vD@ZOU
