OL,3,CMade by a Stone! The artwork by Ronnie
OL,4,CWood that's on display at Longleat
OL,6,F"This has given me so much enjoyment
OL,7,Fas I rarely venture into sculpture."
OL,9,FCeawlin Thynn, the 8th Marquess of
OL,10,FBath, said: "We are delighted to have
OL,11,Fit here in Longleat; it is in the
OL,12,FSecret Garden in an area which is just
OL,13,Fperfect for it ` it looks like it was
OL,14,Fmade to be there.
OL,16,FEmma, the 8th Marchioness, said: "It
OL,17,Fis beautiful. The colours are stunning
OL,18,Fand will change with the seasons as
OL,19,Fthe light bathing it changes.
