OL,3,CMade by a Stone! The artwork by Ronnie
OL,4,CWood that's on display at Longleat
OL,6,FRonnie and Lady Bath are proud
OL,7,Fambassadors of Tusk, and they first
OL,8,Fmet when Lord and Lady Bath purchased
OL,9,Fa gorilla art piece created by
OL,10,FRonnie's wife, Sally.
OL,12,FRonnie said: "Longleat is wonderful. I
OL,13,Fgot involved with Tusk because I want
OL,14,Fmy kids and other people's children to
OL,15,Fbe able to see animals such as rhinos,
OL,16,Flions, tigers. Conservation of these
OL,17,Fanimals is so important to protect
OL,18,Fthem for the future."
OL,26,@tD@NOUzD@UO]
